      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Begin by obtaining API credentials from the Kokoro dashboard. Configure your environment with the base URL "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "https://api.kokoro.ai/v1",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " and set authentication headers using your API key. Ensure your network allows outbound HTTPS traffic to Kokoro endpoints. For testing, use the "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "/health",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " endpoint to verify connectivity before proceeding to inference tasks."
          }
